3 trim-and-fill

### fit random-effects model and plot
datasets = unique(all_data$dataset)

#par(mfrow=c(3,1))
for (i in 1:length(datasets)) {
  my_data = all_data[all_data$dataset ==  datasets[i],]
  res <- rma(d, d_var, data = my_data)
  taf <- trimfill(res)
  funnel(taf, main = my_data$dataset[1])
}
